function Start(idActorKiller, szGroup)

	Hydra.EventSend("LorathWorried")
	Hydra.Wait(5)

	for i, Spawner in ipairs(tAmbush01Wave03Spawners) do

		Hydra.ActorEnable(Spawner)

	end
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	for i, Spawner in ipairs(tAmbush01Wave01Spawners) do

		Hydra.ActorEnable(Spawner)

	end
	
	Hydra.QActorUnsheath(idLorath)
	Hydra.QActorUnsheath(idNeyrelle)
	Hydra.ActorAIOverrideNormalBehavior(idLorath, "Generic_NPC_Combat_NoWander_Leash")
	Hydra.ActorAIOverrideNormalBehavior(idNeyrelle, "Generic_NPC_Combat_NoWander_Leash")

end
